== Development ==
The official OpenEMR code repository was migrated from cvs to git on 10/20/2010.<ref name=git_migrate>{{cite web |url=http://www.open-emr.org/wiki/index.php/Git_Migration |title=OpenEMR Migration to git|accessdate=2012-01-27}}</ref> Currently, the project's official code repository is on Sourceforge.<ref name=sourceforge /> There are also official mirrored code repositories on Github,<ref name=github>{{cite web |url=http://github.com/openemr/openemr |title=OpenEMR on Github|accessdate=2012-12-20}}</ref> Google Code,<ref name=googlecode>{{cite web |url=http://code.google.com/p/openemr |title=OpenEMR on Google Code|accessdate=2012-01-27}}</ref> Gitorious,<ref name=gitorious>{{cite web |url=http://gitorious.org/~openemr |title=OpenEMR on Gitorious|accessdate=2012-01-27}}</ref> Bitbucket,<ref name=bitbucket>{{cite web |url=http://bitbucket.org/openemr/openemr |title=OpenEMR on Bitbucket|accessdate=2012-01-27}}</ref> Assembla,<ref name=assembla>{{cite web |url=http://www.assembla.com/spaces/openemr |title=OpenEMR on Assembla|accessdate=2012-01-27}}</ref> CodePlex<ref name=codeplex>{{cite web |url=http://openemr.codeplex.com/ |title=OpenEMR on CodePlex|accessdate=2012-03-25}}</ref> and Repo.or.cz.<ref name=repo.or.cz>{{cite web |url=http://repo.or.cz/w/openemr.git |title=OpenEMR on repo.or.cz|accessdate=2012-01-27}}</ref>

OpenEMR has a vibrant open-source development community with over 70 developers having contributed to the project.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.open-emr.org/wiki/index.php/Repository_work_flow_structure#Developers |title=OpenEMR Developers|accessdate=2012-12-20}}</ref><ref name=ohlohfactoid>{{cite web |url=http://www.ohloh.net/p/openemr/factoids |title=OpenEMR Factoids on Ohloh|accessdate=2012-06-16}}</ref>  There are 157 developers with personal OpenEMR code repositories on Github.<ref name=github /> Ohloh considers OpenEMR to have "a relatively large team, in the top 10% of all project teams on Ohloh".<ref name=ohlohfactoid />

